{"tid":198910,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[串嘴球王] C朗：拜仁只是我們衛冕的絆腳石，而絆腳石只有一種下場","createTime":"2017-04-12T21:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T05:28:05.000Z","uid":28938,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8227fcfb5324be383efa5a52be5730fc790f4ed3","tid":198910,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:15:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>C朗：拜仁只是我們衛冕的絆腳石，而絆腳石只有一種下場</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vy6941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vy6941.jpg&h=00401cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[5:15] 藉下半場連中兩元，C朗拿度帶領皇家馬德里作客反勝拜仁慕尼黑 2:1，出線四強的機會高唱入雲。<br />\n<br />\n賽後C朗拿度表示，無可否認拜仁的主場威力很強，但皇馬球員的意志亦夠堅韌，因此能夠反勝。<br />\n<br />\n他進一步指出：<strong>「拜仁只是我們衛冕的絆腳石，而絆腳石只有一種下場。」</strong>期望返回主場時可以痛宰對手。"},{"pid":"f4a0b6a5e33a1467922644e467d6eddbc1f1507e","tid":198910,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:16:32.000Z","msg":"source <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee09635255900dd5c4ab40e64c75199fa212b19","tid":198910,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>source <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nor police?"},{"pid":"eb2210c36d53abe383aaf9f180a268c6dc4ff37e","tid":198910,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab5a47d247010a4d4ef90f4fb5a02cdfa58dd49","tid":198910,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"山寨王 刷弱隊<br />\n遇到我皇即刻鳩縮"},{"pid":"acb4a2f1673cbbbe62b2bfc4a22e32be3f64135b","tid":198910,"uid":75570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a0decea769cdb5